title: ‘Survivor’ Season 42, Finale With Parvati Shallow
description:
Tyson and Riley are joined by ‘Survivor: Micronesia’ winner Parvati Shallow to break down the season 42 finale. They chat about the departure of Lindsay and Jonathan as well as the results of the final tribal council meeting. Plus, they debate just how far sincerity will get you in this new era of ‘Survivor’ and give their final thoughts on Maryanne’s win.
Hosts: Tyson Apostol and Riley McAtee
Guest: Parvati Shallow
Producer: Devon Manze
